  "description": "Filter resonance at the edge of self-oscillation — the resonant peak becomes a pitched tone fighting the oscillator for dominance. Drive pushes the filter into feedback. The boundary between filter and oscillator blurs. Bob discovering what happens when the tool becomes the instrument.",
